business school in the ’s while a member of the value investing program mr putnam was under the tutelage of some of the industry leaders in finance and investment management after graduating from columbia business school mr putnam was employed by gabelli  company inc as a research analyst working under mario j gabelli gabelli  company inc is a subsidiary of the publicly traded asset management firm gamco investors nyse gbl with approximately  billion under management mario gabelli is an alumnus of columbia business school and the founder and chairman of gamco investors as a firm gamco investors inc has been one of the leading practitioners of the “value” based investing style the company utilizes intense fundamental research and a longterm investment horizon to generate superior investment returns in his role as research analyst mr putnam was responsible for researching and making investment recommendations for companies in the retail and business service sectors particular focus was given to small and midcap companies company visits and meetings with top management was a fundamental part of the research mr putnam’s investment expertise has been sought in a variety of news and media publications his investment recommendations and reports have been published regularly throughout the financial press and through news distribution services such as bloomberg and thompsonreuters mr putnam founded the talanta investment group llc in  to provide clients with access to the superior investment opportunities available in smaller publicly traded companies he is currently the managing member of the talanta investment group llc   steve a joyce jr mr joyce is a life long resident of guilford county north carolina he and his wife mimi have two daughters and live just north of greensboro since graduating from the university of north carolina at greensboro with a degree in political science mr joyce has spent most of his professional life in financial services he has also been very active in community and civic affairs mr joyce has over  years experience in financial services most of which he spent with smith barney as a financial consultant in his tenure as a financial professional mr joyce worked with a broad array of products and services he was privileged to work with clients concerning their financial affairs and continues to enjoy relationships built during those years mr joyce’s interest in the common good have led him to serve with a number of organizations he has served as a board member of his church where he chaired finance he has also served as president of his civic club the kiwanis club of greensboro mr joyce also serves as board member of the excellence foundation at uncg mr joyce is a member of the advisory board of the salvation army of greensboro   talanta investment group inc all rights reserved about  talanta investment group inc client login about talanta investment group llc over the years talanta investment group llc has generated superior returns for clients by investing in overlooked opportunities in established niche businesses these returns are anchored by a firmwide focus on fundamental research within a valuebased investment framework opportunistic investments are made within the company that drive longterm capital growth and above average rates of return for our clients the investment products offered by the talanta investment group llc represent a unique investment opportunity for our clients and are distinguished by a dedication to provide optimal portfolio construction and management and an adherence to an investment strategy that has outperformed the broader market indices for over  years   contact us   talanta investment group inc all rights reserved about  talanta investment group inc client login about talanta investment group llc over the years talanta investment group llc has generated superior returns for clients by investing in overlooked opportunities in established niche businesses these returns are an